{"tid":831452,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"（ 山竹之禍 ）一入後波我粒泊車sensor 長響 自己修理教學","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T04:44:29.000Z","uid":147858,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f7fca0ff7177e505bf9db60ed53d7fe24abca1d6","tid":831452,"uid":147858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"事源打完風之後 開車一入後波粒sensor 長響。<br />\n之後發覺粒sensor 好似比風入L左入去個bumper到！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唸住今翅仆街了，又要科水比車房升起架車拆bumper攪。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110310_4d88e46b17a52e89db6553cb1768a762.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110310_4d88e46b17a52e89db6553cb1768a762.png&h=6dd63e21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110315_89f75d4009748dc51886fccb4b104eaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110315_89f75d4009748dc51886fccb4b104eaf.png&h=d4d841c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110318_effd68883c440286eefb971ee5e48747.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110318_effd68883c440286eefb971ee5e48747.png&h=d199e030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我雖然打份正苦工專業人士，比得起有餘，但都唔想咩都唔做就比人攪。所以把心一橫試下搏一鋪自己尻整一下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110611_7f4cf67abe518e85b63b7cc765b2e5fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110611_7f4cf67abe518e85b63b7cc765b2e5fb.png&h=4befa3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110617_694cff17be9b270e75dddc1b689e701c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110617_694cff17be9b270e75dddc1b689e701c.png&h=27ec479c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/110624_124f9409713b3bbd24becb1bbed1afa4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F110624_124f9409713b3bbd24becb1bbed1afa4.png&h=d18d951c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實方法都幾簡單(for 左右邊果啲兩粒）<br />\n<br />\n1）先拆左前面下方果啲十九膠板<br />\n2）申隻手入左影下條sensor cable 係邊度<br />\n3）摸到條野之後就隊番對sensor出黎<br />\n<br />\n For 中間果兩點就要拆多少少野<br />\n1）先拆左個十九鬼面膠板 可能要星形鏍絲批 不過我用一支批都開得到<br />\n2）之後都係申手入下面就會搵到條線再推番出黎<br />\n<br />\n完成！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75683b935b879f444ef33828e9346f07b10c52bc","tid":831452,"uid":17910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:14:36.000Z","msg":"Thx for sharing"},{"pid":"68d17f7dcca6ee2c01d2db31afee9d273b47dbc9","tid":831452,"uid":27919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"粒sensor本身係有野固定佢喺個窿度定係就咁sip喺個窿度？<br />\n<br />\n如果本身係要有野固定佢嘅你就咁sip番出黎咪下次一大風少少或者你揸得快嘅佢咪好易又甩番入去囉？"},{"pid":"17704bccbabb5145471308b98a471020ddbdc826","tid":831452,"uid":147858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d17f7dcca6ee2c01d2db31afee9d273b47dbc9","tid":831452,"uid":27919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"粒sensor本身係有野固定佢喺個窿度定係就咁sip喺個窿度？<br />\n<br />\n如果本身係要有野固定佢嘅你就咁sip番出黎咪下次一大風少少或者你揸得快嘅佢咪好易又甩番入去囉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"就咁sip 果款！<br />\n開100左右都唔會甩既！"},{"pid":"6054be2d35ad2bc05c89d4e876b9ddaefa172e97","tid":831452,"uid":27919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17704bccbabb5145471308b98a471020ddbdc826","tid":831452,"uid":147858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68d17f7dcca6ee2c01d2db31afee9d273b47dbc9","tid":831452,"uid":27919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T13:33:53.000Z","msg":"粒sensor本身係有野固定佢喺個窿度定係就咁sip喺個窿度？<br />\n<br />\n如果本身係要有野固定佢嘅你就咁sip番出黎咪下次一大風少少或者你揸得快嘅佢咪好易又甩番入去囉？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"就咁sip 果款！<br />\n開100左右都唔會甩既！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"咁你喺後面加d熱溶膠落去固定佢會唔會好d?"}]}